{
  "texts": [
    "It is important to note that we intentionally selected ambiguous task cases that are prone to conflicts between humans and AI and are challenging for both.",
    "As a result, the accuracy of both humans and AI individually is relatively low.",
    "The error bars represent 95% confidence interval.",
    "(*: 𝑝 <0.05) Figure 7:Figure 8:78Figure 7: Participants' reliance and the appropriateness of their reliance.",
    "(A) Participants' reliance on AI's suggestions was measured by agreement fraction and switch fraction."
  ]
}